**Idea — three pass linear walk**: Since `slots` is already sorted, no full sort needed (O(n) total).

1. Push every interval ending before `newSlot.start` (no overlap).
2. While current overlaps with newSlot (`start <= newSlot.end`), expand `newSlot = [min(start), max(end)]`.
