```javascript
function insertDeliverySlot(slots, newSlot) {
  const out = [];
  let i = 0, n = slots.length;
  let [s, e] = newSlot;
  while (i < n && slots[i][1] < s) out.push(slots[i++]);
  while (i < n && slots[i][0] <= e) {
    s = Math.min(s, slots[i][0]);
    e = Math.max(e, slots[i][1]);
    i++;
  }
  out.push([s, e]);
  while (i < n) out.push(slots[i++]);
  return out;
}
```

**Time**: O(n) — leverages the sorted invariant.
**Space**: O(n) for output.

